Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.63,0:01:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today, as everyday, the sun rises and sets...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Morning blossoms fall flower by flower...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today, as everyday, the sun sets and rises...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flowers bloom throughout the area...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But they are not yesterday's flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't we there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, since the doctor introduced you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you must be one, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm a mushi-shi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look so worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I heard, this is \Ndefinitely my area of expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.87,0:02:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I've heard that term, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.91,0:02:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:49.98,EP Title BG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,0)\p1\blur1}m 0 0 l 950 0 950 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.01,0:02:49.98,EP Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\be1}Those Who Inhale the Dew
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know, Akoya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Across the sea, there's a big, beautiful land...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,where everyone lives happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go there someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, don't look so sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.33,0:03:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Attagirl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, why aren't you getting \Nthe boat closer to the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The tide will change soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This area has complicated currents...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.22,0:03:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The currents are fast and powerful as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We can enter the island only\N on the day of the spring tide...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,for only a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't look easy to get in...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a fisherman or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no fishermen on this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.23,0:04:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because boats can set sail safely\N only one day each month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing but rocks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, there is very little soil, \Nso people on this island are poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all getting by somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,having the "living god" as their emotional support...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Living god"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody's there! Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to give this to the "living god"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,so that she'll heal your illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, get up on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll feel much better soon for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why do we have to hide?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The one I want you to take a look at is that "living god".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She used to be an ordinary human!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is just being duped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Next to her, is her father, \Nthe present head of the household...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyday, a "miracle" happens to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the day that her \Nbelievers can pay their respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Her breathing has completely stopped as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:07.30,Alt,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, breathe in the fragrance deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It will take away your inner pain and illnesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the divine powers of the immortal "living god".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, she returns to the way she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2770)}At dawn, she awakens as though nothing had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It was exactly as you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I admit, I was still surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That cures people's illnesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all a sham!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom died without being healed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,even though we offered nearly our entire harvest to the "living god".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That "living god" worship was started by the headman and his family on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's said the headman's family read the tides
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and were first to land on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, generation after generation of "living god" has appeared in their family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,People heard about it, and gradually began coming here, yearning for a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When one "living god" dies, another appears...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,before even half a year has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As time went on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,some people said...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the "living god's" fragrance cured \Neven their terminal illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was very reluctant to believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Akoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing with an outsider again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1475)}I have important business with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:08:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It was about a month after \Nthe previous "living god" had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember it was on the day \Nof the spring tide, like yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And, since that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,she became that inhuman thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that can't communicate,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...or even remember what happened the previous day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned what it was all about shortly thereafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... so someone recovered from their illness again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How simple those people are that they can be cured just by the power of suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Akoya wasn't a bright child,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but she must be happy to be able\N to do her part for the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't forgive them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So I left to find someone who could help Akoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I left the island, saying I would never return.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If he found out I was back, the headman would be suspicious of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, you're in danger, as well, Ginko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I gotten myself into...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:08:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to give in without doing something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, count me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let me have a look at her soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her pulse is abnormally fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her body temperature, too, is far above normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold the light close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There it is... A mushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An offspring was born and its parent died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The cause is a parasite in the nasal cavity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know if removing it\N will bring her back to normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this girl the only one affected?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There are several others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They're kept in isolation on that promontory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them are like Akoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the old days, people like them turned up once in great while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of the past headmen praised them\N and gave them homes here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,as devout believers who were\N able to be close the "living god".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The families they left behind gave them their blessings,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,believing their bloodline produced someone free from all suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,After all that, we found nothing new.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, didn't she become affected\N on the day of the spring tide?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you think of any place accessible only during the spring tide?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.93,0:11:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The cave at the very tip of the promontory...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy has been attacked by parasites, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,See if you can find some more around this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I found two more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Leave them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I found... a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be okay, Akoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep still.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be over in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Akoya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Na... gi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Akoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... but why did Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Akoya, let's leave the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There're three days left until the next spring tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You must keep the fact that you've been healed a secret from the headman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I love this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Father will admit he was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My leaving will only cause someone else to become the "living god".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you should remove the cause from the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to stop the abuse of mushi on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what happened on the day you became the "living god"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, Father summoned me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.32,0:13:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akoya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look, I picked this just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doesn't it smell wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Breathe it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A flower resembling bindweed blossoms... with a strong fragrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen them in the promontory cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They were blooming in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they the cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, we can't let the headman find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1347)}Akoya, act like you're the "living god" until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Still not feeling like yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow I feel so uneasy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was the "living god",
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I could always close my eyes \Nwith such a feeling of satisfaction
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,when I began to grow older at\N sunset and began to fall asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I'm afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:15:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When I awake, the reality that I left behind yesterday is waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I cringe at the immense amount of time that spreads out endlessly before me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you were living on mushi time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That mushi harmonizes its host's \Nbiological clock with its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All living things have different life spans,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's said the number of heartbeats in their lifetimes are about the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, time runs at a different rate for each.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The life span of that mushi is about a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You experienced that every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, maybe that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Each and every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and every passing hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,felt breathtakingly fresh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When I tried to think...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:15:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't keep up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I always...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1389)}felt fulfilled in my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In another hour or so, we'll be able to go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Akoya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,By this time you should be old and weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Father... I don't know how, but I'm healed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear Nagi is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know where he went, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... today is the spring tide day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Bindweed blossoms in the dark...\N What a strong fragrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So this part is the mushi's nest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess animal hosts must ensure\N better survival of their young...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"Living god"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me where the promontory cave is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, the "living god" spoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I'll explain everything, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.73,0:17:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Save Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you! How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:51.61,Alt,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have much time left, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who continue to use mushi carelessly
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,gradually lose their sanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys will eventually be ruined...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're unfit for handling mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's provoking them... I wonder if he has a plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:14.05,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make a run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:15.36,Alt,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:18.15,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure the bodies don't surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.49,0:18:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He was holding a flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Just like Akoya-dono said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we lost them, but the tide is rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! We'll last another hour at most...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone there... \NI found them! Nagi and his friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey down there! Stand clear! \NWe're going to widen the opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I... killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I picked this just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1016)}Don't look so sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it smell wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Breathe it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Akoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.51,0:19:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me... Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there... I can go on living...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more firmly embedded than the first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Removing it will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...because Akoya only appeared happy from the bottom of her heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...when she was the "living god"...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today, as everyday, the sun rises and sets...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.23,0:20:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Morning blossoms fall flower by flower...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today, as everyday, the sun sets and rises...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:21:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flowers bloom throughout the area...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1450)\i1}But they are not yesterday's flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet today's flowers are just as beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That day, Ginko-san missed the spring tide...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so he stayed on the island for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}During that time, he was able to treat everyone living on the promontory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But each spring tide when the cave was exposed,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}someone became a "living god" once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Several probably don't appreciate the treatment...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, they'll breathe the flowers again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Akoya told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I cringe at the immense amount of time that spreads out endlessly before me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not all that different...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to live for from now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just live a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.47,0:22:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Life will be somewhat easier once you're able to fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Work with others to open up that cave so you can set boats out to sea at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.57,0:22:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have before you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...an infinitely large amount of time.
